\angle AEC \equiv \angle BCD=90^\circ \;\;\text{ and }\;\; \angle EAB \equiv \angle DBC \;\; \text{ and } \;\; \angle ABE \equiv \angle BDC
1200=BC \times AB=BC\times 40\;\; \therefore \;\; BC=\frac{1200}{40}=30
